
babl 0.1.2

    Dynamic; any to any, pixel format conversion library.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Installation instructions:
--------------------------

From a released version the following is the expected method of
installation (or a variation on this theme):

     ------------------------------------------------------------
     foo$ wget ftp://ftp.gtk.org/pub/babl/0.0/babl-0.1.2.tar.bz2
     foo$ tar jxf babl-0.1.2.tar.gz
     foo$ cd babl-0.1.2
     foo/babl-0.1.2$ ./configure && make && sudo make install
     ------------------------------------------------------------


